thread.title: Flu fighters: electric guitar made from doctors' tongue depressors

title: Flu fighters: electric guitar made from doctors' tongue depressors
text:
Flu fighters: electric guitar made from doctors' tongue depressors 3:32pm BST - 01:01
Amateur musician Maciej Walaszek built a working electric guitar from wooden tongue depressors, normally used by doctors to examine patients' mouths and throats. Edward Baran reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
